\begin_layout Problem
Верны ли равенства: 1) 
\begin_inset Formula $Z_{2}\times Z_{3}\cong Z_{6}$
\end_inset

, 2) 
\begin_inset Formula $Z_{2}\times Z_{4}\cong Z_{8}$
\end_inset

?
