\begin_inset Formula $h=y_{1}^{-1}h_{x}y_{1}h_{y}\in N$
\end_inset

 такой, что 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(x_{2}y_{2}\right)=\left(x_{1}y_{1}\right)h$
\end_inset

, а значит 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}y_{1}$
\end_inset

 и 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{2}y_{2}$
\end_inset

