\begin_inset Formula $\left[\varphi\left(g_{1}\right)\right]^{-1}$
\end_inset

, получим 
\begin_inset Formula $e_{F}=\left[\varphi\left(g_{1}\right)\right]^{-1}\varphi\left(g_{2}\right)$
\end_inset

.
 Как было показано в задаче 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "prob:homomorphism-maps-inverse-to-inverse"
plural "false"
