\begin_inset Formula $\varphi\left(g_{1}g_{2}\right)=\left(g_{1}g_{2}\right)^{n}=g_{1}^{n}g_{2}^{n}=\varphi\left(g_{1}\right)\varphi\left(g_{2}\right)$
\end_inset

, то есть 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi$
\end_inset

